<div class="scroll-container">
    <div class="scroll-text">

        <h1>Welcome to Balduran's Codex</h1>

        <p>
            Balduran's Codex is a personal project built to gather, organize, and present detailed build guides,
            item information, and gameplay insights for Baldur's Gate 3. The goal of this site is to provide
            players with clear, practical, and enjoyable resources while celebrating the creativity and depth
            of the game.
        </p>

        <h3>Project Purpose</h3>
        <p>
            This site was created as both a learning project and a passion project. It represents the skills I've
            developed in MySQL, C#, ASP.NET MVC, Razor views, and full-stack application structure. Every page,
            every build, and every feature is part of my journey in becoming a stronger developer.
        </p>


